name: 1st Potate
description:
As promised, here's the 1st time I picked up a 12 hole ocarina. The very first time I played the instrument. Edited the best I can with $4 software tu not sound like a dead cat. Practice makes better, but I don't believe in perfection. The belief in perfection is in itself a flaw, voiding perfection. I'll get better as I practice; this is a benchmark for my improvement. Doesn't get more contrasted than the first time I pick up the instrument.
  By all means, please also consider the art a part of this -- this is a level 4 Deep Dream of one of my better flower photos.
